---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Reputation.com — Enterprise Review Management vs. Simple Testimonials">
  <section style="background:var(--bg-alt); padding:80px 0 60px;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px;">
      <p style="color:var(--primary); font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; font-size:14px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em;">SocialProof vs Reputation.com</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight:800; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:20px;">
        Reputation.com is enterprise software. Your salon is not an enterprise.
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem; color:var(--text-muted); max-width:600px; line-height:1.6;">
        Reputation.com charges $2,000+/month for large multi-location brands. SocialProof gives small businesses a beautiful, simple testimonial tool starting at $0.
      </p>
      <div style="margin-top:32px; display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="https://socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Try SocialProof free</a>
        <a href="#comparison" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; color:var(--text-muted); font-weight:500; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 0;">See the comparison ↓</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="comparison" style="padding:64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem; font-weight:700; text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">How they compare</h2>
      <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:0.95rem;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="border-bottom:2px solid var(--border);">
              <th style="text-align:left; padding:12px 16px; font-weight:700;">Feature</th>
              <th style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--primary);">SocialProof</th>
              <th style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text-muted);">Reputation.com</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Target customer</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">Small businesses</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">Enterprise / multi-location</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--bg-alt);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Free plan</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">✅ Free forever (1 widget)</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">❌ Enterprise pricing only</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Starting price</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">$0 → $9/mo</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">$2,000+/mo</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--bg-alt);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Setup complexity</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">✅ 5 minutes, no sales call</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">❌ Requires sales demo + onboarding</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Embed testimonials on site</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">✅ One script tag</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">⚠️ Complex widget + API</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background:var(--bg-alt);">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Who it's really for</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px;">Solopreneurs to 20-person teams</td>
              <td style="text-align:center; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--text-muted);">100+ location chains</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--bg-alt); padding:64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:1.75rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:24px;">Reputation.com is great — for the Fortune 500</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:24px;">
        Reputation.com is a serious enterprise platform for brands with dozens or hundreds of locations managing reviews at scale: think auto dealership groups, hospital networks, and hotel chains. It does AI-powered sentiment analysis, competitor benchmarking, and reputation scoring across Google, Yelp, Tripadvisor, and 100+ others.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:24px;">
        For a yoga studio owner, a freelance photographer, or a boutique consultant? It's thousands of dollars per month and six-figure implementation costs. That's not a tool mismatch — that's the wrong product category entirely.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:0;">
        <strong>SocialProof is what Reputation.com would look like if it were built for you.</strong> No annual contracts, no implementation fees, no enterprise package. Just a share link to collect testimonials and a widget to display them — live today, not after a three-month onboarding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="padding:64px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px; text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:16px;">You don't need enterprise software.</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:32px;">Free forever for 1 active widget. No sales call, no contract, no setup fee.</p>
      <a href="https://socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.1rem; padding:16px 40px;">Start collecting testimonials →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
